<!-- ========== PROCESS STEPS ========== -->
<section class="lr-section lr-section-bordered lr-fade-in">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lr-process-steps lr-stagger">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="lr-process-step lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-process-step-number">01</div>
        <div class="lr-process-step-content">
          <div class="lr-value-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Discovery & AI Strategy</h3>
          <p>We start by understanding your business, users, and goals. Together we identify where AI creates the most value, whether that's automating workflows, powering intelligent features, or enabling entirely new capabilities. You walk away with a clear AI strategy and technical roadmap.</p>
          <div class="lr-process-highlights">
            <span>Business analysis</span>
            <span>AI opportunity mapping</span>
            <span>Technical roadmap</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="lr-process-step lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-process-step-number">02</div>
        <div class="lr-process-step-content">
          <div class="lr-value-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 20h9M16.5 3.5a2.12 2.12 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Design & Architecture</h3>
          <p>Our designers and engineers work in parallel. We create UX wireframes, visual concepts, and system architecture simultaneously. AI model selection, data pipeline design, and infrastructure decisions are made early so nothing blocks development later.</p>
          <div class="lr-process-highlights">
            <span>UX/UI design</span>
            <span>System architecture</span>
            <span>AI model selection</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="lr-process-step lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-process-step-number">03</div>
        <div class="lr-process-step-content">
          <div class="lr-value-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M16 18l6-6-6-6M8 6l-6 6 6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>AI-Native Development</h3>
          <p>We build with AI-accelerated workflows from the start. Every engineer uses AI coding assistants, automated testing, and intelligent code review. Test-driven development ensures quality. Pull requests get peer-reviewed and AI-scanned before merge. The result: production-ready code shipped 3x faster.</p>
          <div class="lr-process-highlights">
            <span>AI-assisted coding</span>
            <span>Test-driven development</span>
            <span>Automated code review</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="lr-process-step lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-process-step-number">04</div>
        <div class="lr-process-step-content">
          <div class="lr-value-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Deploy & Scale</h3>
          <p>Production isn't an afterthought. We set up CI/CD pipelines, monitoring, DDoS protection, and auto-scaling infrastructure from the beginning. Whether you're on AWS, Heroku, or bare metal, your app launches stable and handles whatever traffic comes its way.</p>
          <div class="lr-process-highlights">
            <span>CI/CD pipelines</span>
            <span>Performance monitoring</span>
            <span>Auto-scaling infrastructure</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 -->
      <div class="lr-process-step lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-process-step-number">05</div>
        <div class="lr-process-step-content">
          <div class="lr-value-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M23 6l-9.5 9.5-5-5L1 18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M17 6h6v6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Iterate & Optimize</h3>
          <p>Launching is just the beginning. We track KPIs, run weekly retrospectives, and continuously improve your product. AI models get retrained, features get refined, and performance gets optimized based on real user data. Your product evolves as fast as your market does.</p>
          <div class="lr-process-highlights">
            <span>KPI tracking</span>
            <span>Weekly retrospectives</span>
            <span>Continuous improvement</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

